# Desktop installers land here.
#
# Drop per-platform Tauri build outputs into this directory (see
# apps/client/src-tauri/BUILD.md):
#   *.dmg / *.app.tar.gz   → macOS
#   *.msi / *.exe          → Windows
#   *.AppImage / *.deb     → Linux
#
# The hosted server scans this dir and exposes /downloads/manifest.json
# automatically, so adding a build is just `cp` + reload.
